    a locale via locale-gen in ramdisk, otherwise gettext is unable
    to translate messages (Bug #3796)
  * clear screen before reboot
  * generate a locale for selected installer language (Bug #3796)
  * create small "helper lib" for installer scripts
  * added new RegExTranslation object for easy translation of debootstrap and apt-get
  * small gui update (Bug #3796)
  * merged success/error message from end.py (Bug #3796)
  * limit length of error messages
  * updated script for updating translation files (Bug #3796)
  * use gettext to translate progress headlines in scripts
  * pay attention to auto_reboot (Bug #3796)

