univention-installer (5.0.24-10) unstable; urgency=low

  * Some join scripts touch(1) the .index.txt file prior
    to using accessing it. In that case the creation of
    the symbolic link fails. To prevent that failure we
    remove the .index.txt file during the join sequence
    on a DC Master. (Bug #14846)

