univention-installer (5.0.13-2) unstable; urgency=low

  * update nameservers and gateway with values obtained via DHCP (Bug #12130)
  * timout of DHCP query after 45 seconds
  * jump to Ok-Button if DHCP query was successfull
  * updated translations
  * improved handling of DHCP failures
  * dhclient-script-wrapper avoids changing the current interface configuration
  * set printk console_loglevel to zero to silence ifconfig messages from kernel

