 -- Sönke Schwardt <schwardt@univention.de>  Thu, 21 Jun 2007 09:03:35 +0200

univention-installer (1.4.6-1) unstable; urgency=low

  * do not complain about /-filesystem on LVM LV
  * "use LVM?" dialog defaults to "yes"
  * parted uses factor 1000 for "MB/KB" whilst LVM uses factor 1024 for "MB/KB" -
    internal processing uses now factor 1024; values given to and read from
    parted are now converted
  * reserved space for LVM metadata overhead is not taken into account while
    calculating available space on PV and VG

 -- Sönke Schwardt <schwardt@univention.de>  Wed, 20 Jun 2007 14:33:34 +0200

